	   <tr><td colspan=2>1) Look at the skill guides, which can be found under various links in the SKILLS&nbsp;&nbsp;(Not the SKILLS strategy discussion) section.<br><br>2) Ever hear of a cleric using a sword? No, I didn't think so.<br><br>3) P.S. Means "Post Script", which is a term used to signify additional text added after a letter has been completed and signed.  In the old days when people didn't have word processors and had to type or write letters out, anything they forgot to put in the body of the letter was added on after the signature with a "P.S."<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
