	   <tr><td colspan=2>Tomatha - I found her yesterday on top of the rock just off shore in the lake. The rock is directly in front of the zone entrance to unrest. Look up on top of it. Completed the quest yesterday - took about 10 hrs. If possible, you should get the help of a high lvl druid or someone that can port (lots of travelling to NPC). I suggest this order - NPC at W Karana to start quest, Goblin drop in Keep, zone to NPC in BB outside port, drop off crazed goblin in BB (these are tough - blue to 35 cleric), drop off ghoul in unrest, zone from bb to lava, get drop off high lvl skellies in dungeon (cant remember name off lava) then run to npc in lava to get bag - combine and voila, one GB.<br><br>Good luck on your quest, it is fun but challenging and takes time and patience.<br><br>Ronanmd, Paladin 23rd season<br>Nomadic Circle<br>Xev Server <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
